{"tid":836664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐盟：香港一國兩制受毀　今日6pm直播　練乙錚 戴耀廷 主講　羅冠聰 梁天琦 游蕙禎 etc 遙距","createTime":"2018-09-25T21:51:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T13:13:32.000Z","uid":47714,"like":56,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"761e14b305a3007294841ada38ec11f2ba0452f0","tid":836664,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T21:51:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKCPForum/posts/2475374592480693\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKCPForum%2Fposts%2F2475374592480693&d=QPh9qvvmeiGxVTY%2FFfJyqjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=0b963485\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKCPForum/posts/2475374592480693</a><br />\n<br />\n26/09/2018 星期三。香港時間6pm Facebook Live ！除了練乙錚，戴耀庭等學者主講，大會將播出Videos 。包括被DQ 議員游蕙禎，梁頌恆， Prof Edward Yiu 及被判入獄6 年的梁天琦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HongKongWatch1/posts/1818962531557545\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHongKongWatch1%2Fposts%2F1818962531557545&d=QPh9qvvmeiGxVTY%2FFfJyqjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=8e0dd028\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HongKongWatch1/posts/1818962531557545</a><br />\n<br />\n26 September 2018 Seminar at the European Parliament Facebook LIVE (Hong Kong Time 6pm/ London Time 11am/ Brussels Time 12:00 noon )<br />\n<br />\nOpening remarks<br />\nMEP Prof Joseph Weidenholzer ( Member of European Parliament; Member of Subcommittee on Human Rights) and MEP Jo Leinen<br />\n<br />\nModerator: Dr Malte Kaeding<br />\n<br />\nBrussels Time:<br />\n12:10-12:35 Panel One: Judiciary Independence in Hong Kong<br />\n12:35-13:00 Panel Two: Freedom of Speech and Academic research<br />\n13:00-13:15 Panel Three: Investment Environment in Hong Kong<br />\n13:25-13:50 Discussion<br />\n14:00 End<br />\n<br />\nSpeakers:<br />\nProfessor Carol Jones<br />\nProfessor Benny Yiu Ting Tai<br />\nProfessor Joseph Yi Zheng Lian<br />\nDr Tim Pringle<